(40, 12, 24, 42, 11, 15, 15, 'by Beelzebub the prince of the devils', 'Accusation of Beelzebub', 'Both passages emphasize the accusation that Jesus casts out demons by Beelzebub, the prince or chief of devils. This connection highlights a consistent challenge to Jesus'' authority from the Pharisees.', 'parallel', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
