(40, 12, 27, 42, 9, 49, 50, NULL, 'Authority Over Demons', 'This connection highlights the theme of casting out devils. Both passages address the authority to expel demons, with Matthew questioning the source of such power and Luke affirming that those who act in Jesus'' name are aligned with Him.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
