(40, 13, 37, 44, 1, 8, 8, 'He that soweth the good seed', 'Connection of Witnessing and Sowing', 'This connection highlights the role of the Son of man in sowing good seed, which can be seen as a precursor to the empowerment of believers to witness. Both passages emphasize the spread of the message, from the initial sowing to the eventual witnessing in all parts of the earth.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
