(40, 20, 2, 11, 3, 6, 11, NULL, 'Understanding and Judgment', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of discernment and understanding in fulfilling one''s responsibilities. In Matthew, the laborers agree on their wages, reflecting a need for clarity in their work, while Solomon seeks wisdom to judge his people effectively.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 20, 2, 11, 18, 12, 12, NULL, 'Labor and Divine Guidance', 'This connection highlights the theme of service and obedience to a higher authority. Both passages emphasize the commitment of individuals to fulfill their roles, whether as laborers in a vineyard or as servants of the Lord.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 20, 2, 14, 34, 3, 3, NULL, 'Seeking and Laboring for God', 'This connection highlights the theme of commitment to a task. In Matthew, the laborers agree to work in the vineyard, while in 2 Chronicles, the young king seeks to purify and serve God. Both passages emphasize the importance of dedication to a purpose.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 20, 3, 54, 5, 13, 13, 'standing idle', 'Idleness and Its Consequences', 'This connection highlights the theme of idleness in both passages. In Matthew, those are described as ''standing idle,'' while in 1 Timothy, idleness leads to negative behaviors such as gossiping.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 20, 3, 20, 19, 15, 15, 'standing idle', 'Connection of Idleness and Consequences', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of idleness. Matthew describes individuals as ''standing idle,'' while Proverbs warns that an ''idle soul shall suffer hunger.'' This connection highlights the negative consequences of being idle.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 20, 3, 26, 16, 49, 49, NULL, 'Idleness and Responsibility', 'This connection highlights the theme of idleness in both passages. In Matthew, those standing idle are called to work, while Ezekiel condemns Sodom for their abundance of idleness and lack of support for the needy.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
