(40, 20, 4, 40, 21, 23, 31, 'into the vineyard', 'Vineyard and Obedience Theme', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of working in the vineyard and the responses to authority. In Matthew 20:4, the call to work in the vineyard reflects the expectation of obedience, which is further illustrated in Matthew 21:28-31 through the parable of the two sons and their differing responses to their father''s command.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
