(40, 20, 4, 46, 6, 11, 11, 'whatsoever is right I will give you', 'Vineyard and Justification Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of being called and receiving what is right. Both passages emphasize the transformation and reward given to those who respond to the call, whether in the vineyard or through justification in Christ.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
