(40, 20, 5, 1, 12, 1, 4, NULL, 'Call and Response Theme', 'Both passages emphasize a call to action, where individuals are summoned to leave their current circumstances for a greater purpose. In Matthew, the repeated action of going out reflects a continuous invitation, similar to Abram''s departure in Genesis.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
