(40, 21, 28, 46, 10, 15, 15, 'go work to day in my vineyard', 'Call to Action and Judgment', 'This connection highlights the theme of responding to a call, as seen in the father''s request to his son in Matthew and the invitation to judge in Corinthians. Both passages emphasize the importance of discernment and action in response to a directive.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 21, 28, 41, 13, 34, 34, 'go work to day in my vineyard', 'Work in the Vineyard', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of work assigned by a master. In Matthew, the father commands his son to work in the vineyard, while in Mark, the man gives authority to his servants for their work.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
