(40, 21, 28, 42, 13, 4, 4, 'go work to day in my vineyard', 'Call to Action and Judgment', 'This connection highlights the theme of accountability in both passages. In Matthew, the call to work in the vineyard suggests a responsibility, while Luke''s mention of those who perished emphasizes the consequences of one''s actions.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
