(40, 21, 31, 40, 7, 21, 21, NULL, 'Connection of Doing the Will', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of doing the will of the Father. In Matthew 21:31, Jesus highlights that those who may seem unlikely, like publicans and harlots, fulfill this will, while Matthew 7:21 stresses that mere verbal acknowledgment is insufficient without action.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 21, 31, 40, 20, 16, 16, NULL, 'Last and First in the Kingdom', 'This connection highlights the theme of reversal in the kingdom of God. Both passages emphasize that those who seem least likely to enter, like publicans and harlots, will be prioritized, aligning with the idea that ''the last shall be first.''', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 21, 31, 45, 3, 19, 19, 'the publicans and the harlots', 'Guilt and Acceptance in God', 'Both passages emphasize the idea of guilt before God and the unexpected acceptance of those deemed sinful. Matthew highlights that publicans and harlots enter the kingdom, while Romans states that all are guilty under the law.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 21, 31, 45, 5, 20, 20, 'the publicans and the harlots', 'Grace and Acceptance of Sinners', 'This connection highlights the theme of grace extending to those considered sinners, as seen in both passages. In Matthew, Jesus indicates that publicans and harlots enter the kingdom of God, while Romans emphasizes that where sin abounds, grace does much more abound.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 21, 31, 54, 1, 13, 16, 'the publicans and the harlots', 'Mercy and Grace for Sinners', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of mercy extended to those considered sinners. In Matthew, publicans and harlots are highlighted as entering the kingdom before the righteous, while in 1 Timothy, Paul identifies himself as the chief of sinners who received mercy. This connection highlights the transformative power of grace for those who repent.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
