(40, 22, 32, 2, 3, 6, 6, NULL, 'God of the Living', 'Both passages emphasize God''s relationship with Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob. Matthew highlights that God is not the God of the dead, reinforcing the living nature of this relationship.', 'theme', 0.43299999999999994, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
