(40, 22, 33, 40, 22, 22, 22, 'astonished at his doctrine', 'Response to Jesus'' Teachings', 'Both passages emphasize the reaction of the multitude to Jesus'' words. In each case, the listeners are astonished or marvel at his doctrine, indicating a profound impact of his teachings.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 33, 41, 6, 2, 2, 'astonished at his doctrine', 'Astonishment at Teaching', 'This connection highlights the theme of astonishment in response to Jesus'' teaching. Both passages emphasize the crowd''s reaction of being ''astonished'' at his doctrine and wisdom.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 33, 41, 12, 17, 17, 'astonished at his doctrine', 'Astonishment at Jesus'' Teachings', 'This connection highlights the reaction of the crowd to Jesus'' teachings in both passages. In Matthew, the multitude is ''astonished'' at his doctrine, while in Mark, they ''marvelled'' at his response, indicating a shared theme of amazement at his wisdom.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
