(40, 22, 45, 66, 22, 16, 16, 'David then call him Lord', 'David''s Lineage and Authority', 'This connection highlights the dual identity of Jesus as both the ''root'' and ''offspring'' of David. In Matthew, the question of how David can call someone ''Lord'' emphasizes Jesus'' authority, while Revelation affirms His lineage and divine status.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
