(40, 22, 45, 45, 9, 5, 5, 'call him Lord', 'Connection of David and Christ', 'This connection highlights the lineage of Christ as both a descendant of David and a figure of divine authority. The question of how David can call Christ ''Lord'' emphasizes the dual nature of Christ''s identity in relation to David''s lineage.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
